CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772824283
OL,3,CMass whale stranding may have been
OL,4,Ccaused by 'difficult birth'
OL,6,FThe mass stranding and death of more
OL,7,Fthan 50 whales on a Scottish beach
OL,8,Fcould have been triggered by a single
OL,9,Ffemale having a "difficult birth", a
OL,10,Fnew report suggests.
OL,12,FAn investigation into the incident on
OL,13,Fthe Isle of Lewis in 2023 suggests
OL,14,F"strong social cohesion" among the
OL,15,Fpilot whales "may have then led the
OL,16,Fentire group to follow the distressed
OL,17,Findividual into shallow waters".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772824283
OL,3,CMass whale stranding may have been
OL,4,Ccaused by 'difficult birth'
OL,6,FOnly one of the 55 whales was
OL,7,Fsuccessfully returned to the water and
OL,8,Fthe remainder either died or were
OL,9,Feuthanised on welfare grounds,
OL,10,Faccording to a report published on
OL,11,FThursday.
OL,13,F"Once stranded, the animals were
OL,14,Funable to refloat themselves due to a
OL,15,Fcombination of surf generated by
OL,16,Fonshore winds and the soft sand
OL,17,Fsubstrate on the beach," the report
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772824283
OL,3,CMass whale stranding may have been
OL,4,Ccaused by 'difficult birth'
OL,6,FThe investigation, supported by the
OL,7,FScottish government and Marine
OL,8,FDirectorate considered other factors
OL,9,Fbehind the stranding.
OL,11,FNo signs of underlying diseases, or
OL,12,Fviral or bacterial infections were
OL,13,Ffound in an examination of the whales,
OL,14,Fwho appeared to be in "good overall
OL,15,Fhealth" with "good nutritional
OL,16,Fcondition despite no indication of
OL,17,Frecent feeding".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772824283
OL,3,CMass whale stranding may have been
OL,4,Ccaused by 'difficult birth'
OL,6,FHaving looked into environmental
OL,7,Ffactors including wind, tide and water
OL,8,Fdepth, investigators said: "The
OL,9,Fshallow, steeply shelving nature of
OL,10,Fthe bay, potentially combined with
OL,11,Fonshore winds present during the
OL,12,Fstranding event, was identified as
OL,13,Fhaving had a potential role in
OL,14,Fhindering the pod's navigation."
OL,16,FThe report says this species is rarely
OL,17,Fseen in inshore waters and that their
OL,18,Fpresence close to Traigh Mhor beach,
OL,19,FTolsta, was a "highly unusual
OL,20,Foccurrence".
OL,26,@zD@UqpzD@\qw
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772824283
OL,3,CMass whale stranding may have been
OL,4,Ccaused by 'difficult birth'
OL,6,FInvestigators say dystocia - a
OL,7,Fdifficult birth typically caused by a
OL,8,Flarge or poorly positioned calf - in
OL,9,Fone mature female "suggests a possible
OL,10,Fsocial trigger for the stranding".
OL,12,F"Strong social cohesion may have then
OL,13,Fled the entire group to follow the
OL,14,Fdistressed individual into shallow
OL,15,Fwaters," the report said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772824283
OL,3,CMass whale stranding may have been
OL,4,Ccaused by 'difficult birth'
OL,6,F"Long-finned pilot whales are highly
OL,7,Fsocial animals, and behavioural
OL,8,Fresponses to disturbance, whether
OL,9,Fnatural (e.g., predators) or
OL,10,Fanthropogenic (e.g., vessels,
OL,11,Funderwater noise) are well documented
OL,12,Fin this species," it added.
OL,14,FDr Andrew Brownlow, lead scientist of
OL,15,Fthe investigation by the Scottish
OL,16,FMarine Animal Stranding Scheme, said:
OL,17,F"If a member of the pod was in
OL,18,Fdistress, this species' well-
OL,19,Fdocumented social cohesion would have
OL,20,Fled others to aggregate closely in a
OL,21,Fprotective response.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772824283
OL,3,CMass whale stranding may have been
OL,4,Ccaused by 'difficult birth'
OL,6,F"In this instance, that behaviour
OL,7,Fappears to have drawn the group into
OL,8,Fthe shallow, sandy bathymetry of
OL,9,FTraigh Mhor, where the bay's gently
OL,10,Fsloping seabed and suspended fine
OL,11,Fsediments may have created an
OL,12,F'acoustic trap', attenuating
OL,13,Fecholocation signals and diminishing
OL,14,Fthe capacity for the group to safely
OL,15,Fnavigate back to deeper water. "
OL,26,@qD@CqpqD@JqwwD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772824283
OL,3,CMass whale stranding may have been
OL,4,Ccaused by 'difficult birth'
OL,6,FHe added: "The Tolsta event is a
OL,7,Freminder that mass strandings are
OL,8,Frarely the result of a single cause.
OL,9,FRather, they emerge at the
OL,10,Fintersection of individual physiology,
OL,11,Fgroup social behaviour and external
OL,12,Fmarine environmental conditions.
OL,14,F"Understanding how these factors
OL,15,Finteract is essential if we are to
OL,16,Fimprove our capacity to anticipate,
OL,17,Finterpret and, where possible,
OL,18,Fmitigate the impacts of a changing
OL,19,Focean."
OL,26,@nD@KOUvD@AOU{D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
